title: How much has Luis Fonsi earned with his hit "Despacito"?

og.title: How much has Luis Fonsi earned with his hit "Despacito"?
og.description:
Answer (1 of 5): Despacito by Luis Fonsi has been streamed a whopping 4.6 billion times and is actually the most streamed song ever.

Unfortunately, it is not likely that this will actually translate into much cash considering what an amazing achievement it is to have your song played so many tim...
